00:03:50.499 --> 00:03:55.159
– love means you’d almost do it for free
– and don’t only because you need to live,

00:03:55.159 --> 00:03:58.629
you need to pay your employees and you want
the business to be able to last into the long

00:03:58.629 --> 00:04:05.620
term. The product or service is what you love
and you love it inordinately. Businesses of

00:04:05.620 --> 00:04:10.279
love are the sort where the owner has scoured
the world for the best kind of flour and wakes

00:04:10.279 --> 00:04:15.819
up excitedly at dawn to check on the progress
of each of the loaves; the aircraft factory

00:04:15.819 --> 00:04:20.150
where the workers think of every plane they
are building like a relative they will always

00:04:20.150 --> 00:04:25.740
care for; the stationery shop where notebooks
and paper are viewed as objects of beauty

00:04:25.740 --> 00:04:30.560
rather than utility; the travel agency that
won’t rest until it knows it clients have

00:04:30.560 --> 00:04:35.560
enjoyed their trips rather than just paid
for them; the sandwich store that views a

00:04:35.560 --> 00:04:44.069
fine avocado and chicken roll as one of the
authentic joys of a tricky life. Businesses run for love are not always successful

00:04:44.069 --> 00:04:48.280
in the standard financial sense of the term.
Some might just be returning a little over

00:04:48.280 --> 00:04:55.270
3% a year. But for these enterprises, money
is only ever a means to a greater, more purposeful

00:04:55.270 --> 00:05:01.370
end. There are huge opportunities to hand
for any would-be entrepreneurs because most

00:05:01.370 --> 00:05:06.730
of the economy is in the hands of people who
don’t love what they are doing. Most law

00:05:06.730 --> 00:05:12.490
firms, dentists’ offices, hotels and bakeries
aren’t in it for love. They may be efficient

00:05:12.490 --> 00:05:17.849
and canny, but they are – ultimately – just
waiting to sell up. We don’t need to be

00:05:17.849 --> 00:05:23.599
very original to succeed, we don’t need
to have invented anything very new; we just

00:05:23.599 --> 00:05:27.689
need – to make sense of our lives and to
make an honest living along the way – to

00:05:27.689 --> 00:05:33.440
offer the world something we love a little
more intensely than most people do. .

